{"TopicId":152064,"ForumId":21,"TopicTitle":"[1.2 stock] B-47 Stratojet with WEAPONS","CreatedByName":"Krog34","CreatedById":160084,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-15T06:54:59Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Krog34","CreatedById":160084,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-15T06:54:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#0000cd;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:48px;\u0022\u003E\u003Ci\u003EB-47 Stratojet\u003C/i\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#0000cd;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:48px;\u0022\u003E\u003Ci\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://kerbalx.com/letmeparkthatforyou/B-47-Stratojet.craft\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EClick to Download\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/i\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022XoxqtVZ.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022562\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/XoxqtVZ.jpg\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo after binge watching lots of war and aviation documentaries, I found myself recreating one of the coolest jets that ever flew in real life. Take a few minutes to take a peak at my replica dropping \u0022nukes\u0022 on \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E, all stock of course!\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:P\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022HXOdRWo.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022562\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/HXOdRWo.jpg\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA side view, showing the 3 engines spooling up on the runway. I like to bind each wing\u0027s engines to seperate\u00A0thrust reverse controls so that I\u00A0can 360 in place on the ground for easy turn arounds.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022HFQDuUh.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022562\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/HFQDuUh.jpg\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA top down shot showing the wide wing span, I think scale-wise, the wings should actually be longer. But these are like version4 on the wing designs, gonna go with these for now\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:rolleyes:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_rolleyes.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:rolleyes:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022miZlsKe.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022562\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/miZlsKe.jpg\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTotally unnecessary, but the Stratojet comes equipped with 6 mini rocket boosters for short take offs. Not unlike the real B-47.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u00227BjQpm3.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022562\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/7BjQpm3.jpg\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFlight is easy, even with a full uneven load!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022snnxHhz.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022562\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/snnxHhz.jpg\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOk, now the goods! Toggle the bay doors to reveal 4 \u0022Nuclear Devices\u0022! I\u0027m quite proud of this one, having tried many versions of bombs with different fin orientations nothing seemed to satisfy me. But,\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nwith a \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003ESAS\u003C/abbr\u003E unit and tiny probe core, the short battery life holds the bombs in the correct orientation all the way to the target. Who needs BD Armory anyways!\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E\u00A0Also, you can see the RASCAL guided\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nmissile. Be sure to \u0022control from here\u0022 on the probe unit to correctly orient the Nav Ball while flying the RASCAL.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022a6lP6Eb.jpg?1\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022562\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/a6lP6Eb.jpg?1\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBombs away!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022r5mk3iV.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022562\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/r5mk3iV.jpg\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n2 more drops\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022GECNBv9.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022562\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/GECNBv9.jpg\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n1 direct hit!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u00227SMtMHJ.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022562\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/7SMtMHJ.jpg\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n1 near hit!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Q4PYNLT.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022562\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/Q4PYNLT.jpg\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n6 wheesly engines are powerful enough to put this large jet into a loop while still loaded with the RASCAL, time for a second attack run!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022zZclHOR.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022562\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/zZclHOR.jpg\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFOX 1!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022e5m9Orm.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022562\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/e5m9Orm.jpg\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe RASCAL missile is very fast and fairly manuerable\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022iTfdCcm.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022562\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/iTfdCcm.jpg\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDirect hit!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022LBvfaLq.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022562\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/LBvfaLq.jpg\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOne final attack run in an attempt to knock any building down! But what do we have left to attack with...?\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:0.0:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_shocked.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:0.0:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022HbI9t16.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022562\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/HbI9t16.jpg\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAuxiliary fuel tanks go!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Rk083Jt.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022562\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/Rk083Jt.jpg\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo dice \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:(\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_sad.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:(\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022cZ4eSkT.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022562\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/cZ4eSkT.jpg\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA final loop to head back to the runway, feeling much more powerful with a lot of extra weight dropped.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022dnqQbmd.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022562\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/dnqQbmd.jpg\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBicycle style landing gear emulates the real plane, but I\u0027ve added some help for easier landings\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022dDssd9e.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022562\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/dDssd9e.jpg\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDon\u0027t mind their terrified faces, it was a smooth landing.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks for reading this far, please download the B-47 for yourself and bomb \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E too! Post your pics on here as well, I\u0027d like to see what you guys do with my jet! \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-11-15T06:58:53Z\u0022 title=\u002211/15/2016 06:58  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003ENovember 15, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Krog34\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"klond","CreatedById":38787,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-15T23:10:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0Wings angled down, bigger gear in the center, takeoff-assist rockets - looks proper, good job!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u002206c156b6bb1546a9771ed43d31472682.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022750\u0022 src=\u0022https://s-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com/originals/06/c1/56/06c156b6bb1546a9771ed43d31472682.jpg\u0022 width=\u0022954\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Krog34","CreatedById":160084,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-17T06:43:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222852123\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022152064\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221479251448\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002238787\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022klond\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 11/15/2016 at 3:10 PM, klond said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0Wings angled down, bigger gear in the center, takeoff-assist rockets - looks proper, good job!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks! She flys like a dream, it\u0027s funny how little work you have to do when you copy real life designs haha. For the most part the aerodynamics translate over to KSP well.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Torquimedes","CreatedById":137645,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-18T21:38:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOutstanding replica!\u00A0\u00A0 Very impressive.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nQuick question:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nQuote\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut, with a \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003ESAS\u003C/abbr\u003E unit and tiny probe core, the short battery life holds the bombs in the correct orientation all the way to the target. Who needs BD Armory anyways!\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs this stock behaviour?\u00A0 Any stock missile I launch has its \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003ESAS\u003C/abbr\u003E disabled and just tumbles.\u00A0 I\u0027ve had to use dumb rockets with spin fins instead, which do horrible things to the handling of the aircraft they\u0027re mounted to.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}